    "Ce paquet propose un assistant de désinstallation dans DSM. DSM Access ne lancera pas sa désinstallation sans cet assistant." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "This package provides an uninstall assistant in DSM. DSM Access will not uninstall it without that assistant."
